dump two public key
```
$ RsaCtfTool --dumpkey --key pub1.pub
[*] n: 
[*] e: 65537

$ RsaCtfTool --dumpkey --key pub2.pub
[*] n: 
[*] e: 65537
```

guess N1, N2 use the same p, calculate gcd(N1, N2)
```
>>> p = gcd(n1,n2)

```
